<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>11236</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>16855</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>住持叫来了两个和尚。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>16856</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>20025</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们迅速跑进了房间。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>20026</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>24507</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“有什么事吗，住持？”一个和尚问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>24508</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>29646</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我不能把这件袈裟还给唐僧。”住持说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>29647</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>35077</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但您必须把它还回去啊。”另一个和尚说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>35078</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>41739</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这件袈裟是佛祖的宝贝。”住持说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>41740</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>44843</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“它来自西天极乐世界。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>44844</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>50635</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>作为佛教徒，我们必须尽全力把它留在我们的寺院里。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>50636</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>55976</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“唐僧不会把它留给你的。”第一个和尚说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>55977</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>61798</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>住持微笑了。他的眼睛闪过了邪光。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>61799</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>65127</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我有一个计划。”他说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>65128</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>70828</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空一直没睡，在房顶上打坐。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>70829</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>74589</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>就在那时，他听到了脚步声。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>74590</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>80650</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他向下看去，结果看到了两个和尚走过了庭院。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>80651</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>84103</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们举着成捆的柴火。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>84104</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>90423</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“都已经半夜了。”悟空想，“他们为什么要点火？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>90424</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>96326</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>和尚们把柴火堆在了唐僧睡觉的房子外面。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>96327</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>102044</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“啊哈！”悟空想，“这住持想要留着我们的袈裟。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>102045</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>104523</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他计划杀了我们。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>104524</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>114138</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空一直等到和尚们把柴火点燃，然后他使用了法术。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>114139</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>121776</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>和尚们尖叫着四处逃跑，庭院里到处都是火。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>121777</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>128023</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>有间屋子烧着了，然后另一间屋子也烧了起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>128024</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>133088</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>很快，寺院里大多数屋子都烧着了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>133089</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>138961</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>墙壁都倒塌了，屋顶也塌了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>138962</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>143378</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“快逃命吧！”一个和尚大叫。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>143379</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>148321</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们的寺院着火了！”另一个和尚说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>148322</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>154473</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然而，有间屋子在这样的大火里却平安无事 。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>154474</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>162595</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>唐僧在屋子里安然地睡着，而寺院里的其他地方都烧光了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>162596</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>168312</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>第二天一早，唐僧醒了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>168313</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>174830</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他打开门一看，大吃一惊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>174831</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>177528</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>空气中弥漫着浓烟。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>177529</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>182330</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>被烧毁的木头在地上堆成了堆。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>182331</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>187460</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>各间屋子的墙都被烧黑，烧毁了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>187461</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>193928</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“噢，天啊！”唐僧大叫，“寺院里出了什么事情？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>193929</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>196330</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他转过身来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>196331</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>202921</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这时候他意识到自己睡的那间屋子是没事的。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>202922</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>212261</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空走过来。“悟空！”唐僧大叫，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>212262</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>214846</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这里出什么事情了？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>214847</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>218458</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“住持想要杀了你。”悟空说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>218459</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>222376</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他在你住的这间屋子里放火。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>222377</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>229766</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>唐僧不明白：“但这间屋子没事啊，火没烧到这里来。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>229767</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>235599</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空笑了：“我用我的法术挡住了大火。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>235600</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>241720</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>唐僧挠了挠脑袋：“其他的屋子都被烧毁了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>241721</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>247244</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我也用我的法术烧了这些屋子。”悟空微笑着说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>247245</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>252246</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我使了个咒语，只保护你住的这间屋子和袈裟，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>252247</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>256380</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但那咒语让大火烧到了其他的地方。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>256381</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>259718</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>唐僧的眼睛里满是泪水。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>259719</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>262449</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他看上去很生气。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>262450</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>266996</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这太可怕了，悟空！”他大叫，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>266997</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>271956</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“如果你有能力阻止大火，你就应该把火灭掉！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>271957</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>278924</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空耸耸肩：“这里的和尚都是坏人。他们罪有应得。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>278925</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>283438</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>就在这时他们听到一声尖叫。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>283439</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>286398</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>两个和尚向他们冲过来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>286399</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>292121</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“可恶！”悟空大叫，“你们居然敢放火烧我的师父！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>292122</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>296387</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我就应该用我的金箍棒打你们！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>296388</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>299727</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那两个和尚跪在地上磕头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>299728</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>303966</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“请原谅我们吧！”一个和尚大叫，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>303967</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>308363</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们不想伤害你，也不想伤害唐僧的！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>308364</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>311983</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>都是住持的主意！他才是坏人！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>311984</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>315836</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空瞪了这两个和尚一会儿。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>315837</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>318549</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后，他放松了下来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>318550</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>322562</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“起来吧！”他说，“我相信你们。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>63</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>322563</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>327636</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>去把袈裟拿来，我们还要继续去西天取经呢。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>64</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>327637</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>332716</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们......我们不能。”一个和尚说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>65</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>332717</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>340623</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他浑身发抖：“那袈裟不见了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>